Description 
In our standard investment package, you can buy an investment slot for as low as 50,000 Naira for a return as high as 45% per annum on your investment.  You can also have multiple investment slots. The good thing about the investment package is that it can be liquidated at any time after three months of subscription. 

Features:

1. Up to 45% ROI per annum.
2. Monitor investment from your mobile.
3. Liquidate investment anytime.
4. We bear your risks.
5. An investor may have multiple plans.
6. Plan can run concurrently with other investment plans.
7. Monthly access to profit.
8. Get huge reward for referring others.

9. If liquidated before three months 20% will be deducted from subscriber's capital.


Only a few slots are available.
Eligibility: Anyone is eligible to partake in this investment package.

This package makes investments easier for you by buying a slot for as low as 2,000 Naira. You can have unlimited number of slots and gradually build a strong portfolio earning you up to 40% Return on Investment per annum. There is a huge power in smallness, do not wait till you have big monies, start investing now with this micro package and unlock your earning ability. To start investing, please click the button on the right side.

While being a student can be financially demanding, you can regardless, begin to build a financial portfolio for yourself for a good head start right after school. You should not wait until you get a job or have a huge amount of money before you begin to invest. Start investing with the little you have now and watch your portfolio grow.

Start building your youngsters' financial future by training them on financial intelligence and making a huge savings for them. This package is designed for children investments so that they have some savings working for them as they grow. Buy unlimited number of slots for your kids in your own profile or simply create their respective profiles and watch it grow. It is an affordable investment you will be happy you subscribe to.

Description.  
This is an investment package for the Military targeted at investors who can save their investments over a period of 24months. In this package, the investor buys a slot for a minimum of 25,000 Naira only, leaves the investment for a further 24 months for a return of 220% of investment capital.

 


Features:
1. Maturity tenure of 24 months.
2. Up to 220% ROI on maturity.
3. An investor may have multiple plans.
10. The plan can run concurrently with other investment plans.     
11. Monitor investment from your mobile.
12. Premature termination of investment results in 20% loss of capital.
13. Get a reward for referring others.

Only few slots available.

Description

We understand the variation in risk appetite, so we have a package that may suit your appetite. If you want to invest in any of our project and you find none of our packages suitable for you, you can discuss a mutually beneficial business relationship with us. We can come to terms regarding your specific investments needs, provided it is feasible and leads to a Win-Win relationship. Our partnership may exceed financial investments to business to business partnership for mutual profitability.
 
Features.
1. Highly flexible Win-Win Business Relationship.
2. Clients Oriented.
3. Can run concurrently with other investments packages.
 
Eligibility: Military persons are eligible to partake in this package.

As a youth corper, you secretly may be having fears about what the future holds after the Service, well, while your allowance may be meagre, you can start to build a starting pedestal for yourself post service. With just 5,000 Naira for a slot, you can earn up to 40% return on investment per annum.

Basal Plans - 360

Description:
The basal package is an affordable contributory package that allows sponsorship with as low as 500 Naira only per day. The package allows for daily contribution for a year (365 days).  Like other contributory packages, this package has the contribution phase of one year and the incubation phase of One month.  During the contributory phase, the Sponsor continues to contribute 500 Naira daily to his portfolio he may also chose to do it weekly or fortnightly (It is better to pay ahead). The profit calculation will only be based on contribution balance. Please note that during the contribution phase, the sponsor may still liquidate his package at a surcharge of 15% of balance.

Features:

  • Easy to setup.
  • 25.56 Return on Investment in 13 Months.
    Contributory Sponsorship Package.
    Minimum contribution as low as 500 Naira daily.
    Contributory term of 12 months.
    Maturity tenure of 13 months.
    To maximize profit, Sponsors are implored to be consistent in daily contributions.
  • Plan can run concurrently with other plans.
  • Monitor your packages from your mobile.
    Premature termination results in 15% loss of balance. 
    Termination after Contributory phase attracts no penalty. 
  • Get huge reward for referring others.
    Life insurance worth of the total contribution made.       
    Accident insurance of up to 10% of contribution target.  

 

Please click here to download brochure for this package.

Please click here to download the profit spread sheet for this package.

Description
The Maestro Package is made for those who are about to go into retirement. It is a contributory package in which the person contributes his investments over a period (Max 5 years) for a continuous return on investment for a period of up to 20 years. The investor can set his target monthly Pay, contribution amount or time frame as it suits him. It is a highly flexible package that can be made to suit individual’s needs. The investor may decide how much he wishes to contribute monthly over a certain period, otherwise, he may decide how much he wishes to receive and how often he wishes to from his investments and for how long.

Features:

1. Easy to setup.
2. Investment is a contributory investment package.
3. Minimum contribution as low as 25,000 Naira or equivalence.
4. Contributory term from 0 - 12 months.
5. Maturity tenure of 36 months.
6. Investor may make investment at once without contribution, thus reducing maturity tenure to 24 months.
7. Monthly pay to 420% of your monthly contribution for 20 years.
8. Investor must be consistent not to default in monthly contribution.
9. Investment reverts to Standard automatically if client defaults.
10. An investor may have multiple plans.
11. Plan can run concurrently with other investment plans.
12. Monitor investment from your mobile.
13. Premature termination of investment during contributory phase results in 15% loss of balance.
14. Termination after Contributory phase attracts no penalty.
15. Get huge reward for referring others.

Only few slots available.

Eligibility: This package is opened to anyone.
